---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us">
	<div class="bg-gray-50 py-12 sm:py-20">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">About Phora Inc.</h1>
                <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">Delivering "Total Control" in Animal Production since 2015.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-16">
                <!-- Company Overview -->
                <section class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4 flex items-center">
                         <span class="bg-teal-100 p-2 rounded-lg mr-3 text-primary">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" /></svg>
                        </span>
                        Who We Are
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        Established in 2015, Phora Inc. combines over <strong>30 years of experience</strong> in the animal health and nutrition sector. We are proud to be the official distributor for <strong>Arm & Hammer Animal Nutrition</strong> in Turkey, bringing global innovation to local producers.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                        Our core markets include Turkey, with established partnerships extending to the USA and India.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <!-- Mission -->
                <section class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4 flex items-center">
                        <span class="bg-teal-100 p-2 rounded-lg mr-3 text-primary">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" /></svg>
                        </span>
                        Our Mission
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-lg font-medium mb-4">
                        "To develop solutions to control major challenges of animal producers."
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                        We focus relentlessly on <strong>gut welfare</strong>, enabling <strong>antibiotic-free production</strong>, and achieving <strong>performance optimization</strong>. We believe in science-based approaches to solve the industry's toughest problems.
                    </p>
                </section>

                 <!-- Technology -->
                <section class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4 flex items-center">
                         <span class="bg-teal-100 p-2 rounded-lg mr-3 text-primary">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.384-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z" /></svg>
                        </span>
                        Technology: RFCs
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                        Our solutions utilize <strong>Refined Functional Carbohydrates™ (RFCs™)</strong> technology. Unlike standard yeast culture products, RFCs are enzymatically refined to unlock specific bio-active functional benefits that help animals cope with health challenges.
                    </p>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg text-center">
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Block Pathogens</h3>
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Suppresses colonization of harmful bacteria like E. coli and Salmonella.</p>
                        </div>
                         <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg text-center">
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Support Immunity</h3>
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Prepares the immune system to respond quickly to threats.</p>
                        </div>
                         <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg text-center">
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Feed Efficiency</h3>
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Improves nutrient absorption and gut structure.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
